    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The style and culture of a division of the Sioux people formerly inhabiting northern Minnesota, now located mainly in North and South Dakota and eastern Montana.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
